  "created": "2026-03-16",
  "description": "Blend fixed at 0.55 — perception slightly dominant, memory still audible beneath, two voices in productive tension. Mod wheel blurs the boundary: at low throw it remains a clean dual-narrative; at full throw, blend tips toward pure perception while interference rises, the two streams colliding at maximum intensity, the overtones of their disagreement becoming a third voice. This is not a crossfade — it is an argument. Aftertouch intensifies interference directly: pressing into a held chord amplifies the beating between memory and perception streams, the collision frequency shifting as you vary pressure. Each pressure plateau is a different acoustical interference pattern. Velocity controls reactivity — soft touch leaves memory stable; hard strike activates full reactivity, the memory layer instantly responding to transient content, the gap between the two narratives widening on impact.",
